  "remarks": "\nROCKY RUNNER (IMO 9288899) is involved in activity whose object or effect is to destabilise Ukraine or undermine or threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine or to obtain a benefit from or support the Government of Russia. Namely, ROCKY RUNNER is involved in carrying oil or oil products from a place in Russia to a third country. \n",
